column1: Which team will win the 2017 College Football Playoff National Championship?
column6: ['Sports']
column11: This question was closed with the correct answer "Clemson" with an end date of 9 January 2017. Clemson defeated Alabama in the 2017 College Football Playoff National Championship (ESPN). See our FAQ to learn about how we resolve questions and how scores are calculated.
